    p To learn more about ARK:
    a(href="https://n2t.net/e/ark_ids.html") see here.
    p Example:
    p Base URL/tx will redirect to the appropriate URL on arweave.net
    p example is:
    a(href="https://arweave-ark.glitch.me/0TR0dihcC17Plk8VOJUs9PZkzpnlbMFBKayTwugTB3E") https://arweave-ark.glitch.me/0TR0dihcC17Plk8VOJUs9PZkzpnlbMFBKayTwugTB3E
